<HEADLINE>
FT  12 MAY 93 / UK Company News: Contra-Cyclical
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The net asset value per capital share of Contra-Cyclical Investment Trust
was 43.7p at the March 31 year-end, up from 34.7p for the previous period
from February 26 1991 - the date of incorporation - to end-March 1992.
Values for income shares and zero dividend preference shares rose from 3.7p
to 4.9p and from 55.8p to 62.3p respectively.
Attributable revenue was static at Pounds 1.1m, for earnings of 13.92p
(13.94p) per income share. A recommended final dividend of 6p brings the
total for the year to 12.75p (11.25p).
