Belgium                (115.1)       114.8       41,868
Ireland                 (98.2)       104.1       40,435
Portugal                (79.0)       100.4       34,314
 ------------------------------------------------------------------
That should cheer up the Swiss a little, besides deterring the Germans from
crowing too much.
